Please note: each participant has 2 rows: 1 for each block. Block 1 = Stroop AP	 block 2 = Stroop PA (see fMRI data). Task timing info (e.g.	 ISI's etc.) will be included with BIDS-ified fMRI unprocessed data in "events" csv's. The total number of trials is given by strooptotacc + strooptoterr + scwt_omission (per block should equal 78 trials each). Total mean percent correct (per block) in acc column.
